Sergey:

Thanks for your work on flashcards.  Practice is what everybody needs to 
develop fluency in reading QS.  Your flashcards can help to develop that 
automatic fluency.  I just ran through the alphabet to see how it works.

I can see that using this program with a deck of common words could be 
very helpful in promoting QS literacy.

By the way, the Thoth font does have No. 20 (whitewheat):  it is mapped 
to the ~ key.  So you should include it in your flashcard set.

Paige

